Abuja – Aunty Maureen appears prepared for the next man as she flaunts her cleavage to mark her birthday. Birthday woman and estranged wife of Nollywood actor, Blossom Chukwujekwu took to her Instagram page moments ago to share this mind blowing photo. Maureen Esisi shared the cleavage-baring photo with a very lengthy caption which detailed in two parts, first to thank her fans and well wishers for the gifts and birthday messages. Second part is her talking more about her business brands and soliciting her fans to patronize her business if they truly love her. She said: “Thank you to Everyone Who Wished me Well Yesterday….it was truly Overwhelming.. the Outpour of love, the Huge Support on my New Plug @revive_red Thank you” Source